<plot>GILLERY'S LITTLE SECRET is a female-driven examination of the depth that lies between love and friendship. Gillery Poiencot returns home for her 20th high school reunion. While there, she is confronted by a young girl seeking answers that she believes only Gillery can resolve. However, her journey to answer these questions forces her to confront a past love, uncovering a hidden secret only now forced into the light after eighteen years.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?214960</url></doc>
